The paper deals with graph parameters and their impact on solving hard graph problems efficiently. This falls under the category of Discrete Mathematics (cs.DM) and Graph Theory (cs.GT). The paper also discusses the complexity of various graph problems, which is related to Computational Geometry (cs.CG) and Complexity Theory (cs.CC). Finally, the paper proposes a new graph parameter, which is related to Data Structures (cs.DS).
